## Objective
This project performs Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) on a retail transactions dataset to uncover patterns, anomalies, and business insights related to revenue, profitability, discounts, and customer behavior.

## Dataset Overview
The dataset contains transactional-level retail sales data including:

- Order details
- Pricing & discounts
- Revenue & cost metrics
- Profitability indicators
- Customer & regional attributes


